General.Name: Newmark REIT Management Ltd Unit
General.Description: Newmark Property REIT ('NPR') is a stapled group comprising the Newmark Hardware Trust ('Hardware Trust') and the Newmark Capital (Chadstone) Property Trust ('Chadstone Trust'). NPR was formed on 7 December 2021. Aiming to deliver consistent and growing income distributions, Newmark Property REIT offers investors access to well-located, high-quality Australian hardware and large-format retail properties leased mainly to Wesfarmers subsidiary, Bunnings.
